            , was indicted for <rs id="t18130602-66-off348" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130602-66-off348" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130602-66-off348" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130602-66-cd349" type="crimeDate">13th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-66-off348 t18130602-66-cd349"></join>, three bed-curtains, value 10 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18130602-66-victim657" type="victimName">
                     Peter 
                     Denys
                  <interp inst="t18130602-66-victim657" type="surname" value="Denys"></interp>
