               GUILTY
            </rs> - <rs id="t18130602-66-punish352" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130602-66-punish352" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-66-defend654 t18130602-66-punish352"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 26.</p>
